	<h2>Three workflows, one API</h2>
	<ul>
		<li><strong>For real-time call setup</strong> — Sub-200ms LRN/MNP lookup at signup time, fraud-check time, or call-setup time. REST and webhook formats.</li>
		<li><strong>For ops teams</strong> — Portal lookup with shareable URLs and exportable history. No API key required for users with portal access.</li>
		<li><strong>For batch hygiene</strong> — CSV upload, results in minutes for lists up to 100k numbers. Per-query rate the same as the API.</li>
	</ul>
</section>

